.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, fantasy, martial-arts, satire
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, collecting, reading, skydiving, card-games
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: thrillermaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the british is the person watching fantasy movies
2. the swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the danish is the person who's hobby is skydiving
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies
5. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is collecting
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the bird
7. the person watching satire movies is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the thrillermaster-smoker is the person who's hobby is drawing
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Movie-Genre		|    satire	|     thriller	|      fantasy	|     mystery	|     martial-arts	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Hobby	|    card-games	|     skydiving	|     reading	|    collecting	|      drawing	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   thrillermaster	|
